comment._content: Dietlof von Arnim-Boitzenburg (* 22. August 1867 in Berlin; † 15. April 1933 in Boitzenburg) de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dietlof_von_Arnim-Boitzenburg (in German). He was the last president of the Prussian House of Lords (Preussisches Herrenhaus), from January 13, 1916 to November15, 1918.
